This package contains various routines for drawing ellipses and
ellipse-like confidence regions, implementing the plots described
in Murdoch and Chow (1996), A graphical display of large correlation
matrices, The American Statistician 50, 178-180. There are also
routines implementing the profile plots described in Bates and Watts
(1988), Nonlinear Regression Analysis and its Applications.

WWW:	http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/ellipse/
